data.description: Tucked away in the heart of Atascadero lies this 2,500 sq. ft. split-level home enveloped in a natural setting. Situated among the Oak trees and hillside charm the home is perfectly situated to enjoy the deck and tranquility of your surroundings. The split-level home offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, open concept living room and kitchen, laundry room and attached 2 car garage. From the front entry the first floor features vaulted ceilings and lovingly designed living space with fireplace, direct access to the deck and spacious kitchen while the second floor includes bedrooms and master suite. The expansive deck overlooks the beauty of the terrain of the 4.6± acres and private trailhead access. An enchanting private hillside retreat with tree coverage and seamless indoor-outdoor living.
